    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__5180.
_:b0__5180 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2099-12-31"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2001-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
