    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2026-05-08"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "1995-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>, <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/728cbad6-b063-40de-b07c-4ce027f4614b> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/klimatolog_smhi.se>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-view.smhi.se/met-obs/ACMF.nederbord_intensitet_view/wms?service=wms&request=getcapabilities>, <https://opendata.smhi.se/metobs/api>, <https://www.smhi.se/data/hitta-data-for-en-plats/ladda-ner-vaderobservationer/precipitationIntensity15MinutesMax>, <https://opendata-download-metobs.smhi.se/api/version/latest/parameter/15.json>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2014-09-30"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
