<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#0a76b049848b58d7bd17037a8c28b971>.
<#0a76b049848b58d7bd17037a8c28b971> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/e1faa8e1-77ad-4716-8266-e3c359e043eb>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-05-08T06:37:05.558Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#0a76b049848b58d7bd17037a8c28b971> {
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/e1faa8e1-77ad-4716-8266-e3c359e043eb> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Is"@sv, "Öppna data"@sv, "Observation"@sv, "Oceanografi"@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/IRREG>;
