<https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/9e1b1690b4fc73633bd8b9b6908acd07> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__9329.
_:b0__9329 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/2a67b0e20138509958ecf64d4e0236ba>;
