    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Photogrammetric 3D model of an Early Neolithic polygonal stone axe collected from Skåne and held in the collections of the National Historical Museums in Stockholm.\n\nLink to the Dynamic Collection platform  \n\nhttps://dyncoll.ht.lu.se/artifact_view.php?item=694\n\nLink to Sök I Samlingarna  \n\nhttps://samlingar.shm.se/object/9093CDFD-7ED0-4AC4-9F54-44670BBCD57D"@en;
