_:b0__1948 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/author>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/de9b2c906379566cc03a08aa0110dabf>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/002794> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/NON_PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE5561213066>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A major part of this survey is a replication of earlier surveys. Questions about life style and decisional power at work are back again after being removed the year before. New questions deals with how much of the content the respondent reads in different papers\n\nPurpose:\n\nCollect broad information about interests, purchasing habits and media choices"@en, "A major part of this survey is a replication of earlier surveys. Questions about life style and decisional power at work are back again after being removed the year before. New questions deals with how much of the content the respondent reads in different papers\n\nSyfte:\n\nSamla in en bred information om intressen, köpvanor och mediaval"@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://sws.geonames.org/2661886>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.5878/002794#distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "1985-01-01T00:00:00Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
