<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#ab3142f96de14f84dd7ce305d0a92808>.
<#ab3142f96de14f84dd7ce305d0a92808> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://catalog.gavle.se/store/1/resource/444>;
